          "content": "Motilal Oswal Financial Services is one of the most diversified capital-markets franchises in India, with a structurally improving mix of annuity-style asset management and wealth fees offsetting cyclicality in broking and investment banking. The next leg of growth is being driven by strong client additions, AUM compounding in AMC and PWM, and operating leverage in housing finance."
